<plot>Jack Chen is sent to New York to work as a delivery boy in his uncle's Chinatown store in order to forget a bittersweet love affair. While indulging his sadness, Jack can't help but to be drawn to his lively, but ill-reputed, roommate, Lana Lin. After passing judgement on Lana's loose lifestyle, Jack finds himself desiring her. However, Lana's seduction of Jack ends up crossing over to vengefulness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?076330</url></doc>
